{"tid":1399753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實啲柒警開電筒唔係為乜野 係因為佢地睇唔到路","createTime":"2019-08-03T09:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T09:50:25.000Z","uid":272968,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c245312158dd723cfa733c7d4926984db8964fae","tid":1399753,"uid":272968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:31:41.000Z","msg":"我諗左一陣點解佢地係唔係都要鳩開電筒 <br />\n明明好多時候條街都有足夠照明<br />\n而且佢知佢枝電筒響有足夠照明嘅街道上其實冇乜作用<br />\n又眾所鳩知佢地DIY貼左啲玻璃反光膜落塊鏡到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>就好似你地班弱撚智將以為遮左光就可以擋到強光咁</strong></span><br />\n但你要知遮唔係遮一時<br />\n係遮一世<br />\n佢地可能聰鳩明買左啲50%遮光率嘅反光膜<br />\n一貼撚左落去呢<br />\n就條街本來好光嘅都睇落黑媽媽連腳都睇唔到<br />\n咁佢係迫住開電筒照路<br />\n<br />\n相反<br />\n佢眼中風景其實就同黑暗幽谷一樣<br />\n你諗吓夜晚熄哂燈跟住開手機<br />\n一個手殘㩒左100%亮度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地自己參透吓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我冇野講<br />\n我要見律師"},{"pid":"4bfea81904e66ae22aebfd6a68f0f9a53bcab54d","tid":1399753,"uid":272968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:36:37.000Z","msg":"閱讀門檻：IQ100"},{"pid":"47a0a7d3a67b5e1397e6420d8eaba65897145e1b","tid":1399753,"uid":20554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:50:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}